name: Vol 1., Ch.1: New Beginings
description:
Finally, it’s first week of college for Tiara. A scary day! After being raised in a girls-only catholic school at home, moving to the big-city university seems like a big change, but also an exiting opportunity to meet new friends, and perhaps even a boyfriend.

To reduce the anxiety, Tiara prepares for her first day by waking up early, completing the morning exercise routine, and putting on her best makeup. “I know its only school,  but I better make a good impression!” she says to herself.
